Package: benjaminileaves
Title: Generate ficus benjamina leaf shapes with bezier curves
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Urs",
           family = "Wilke",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "urs.wilke@gmail.com")
Description: This package can be used to generate shapes in the form of ficus benjamina (weeping fig) leaves with bezier curves. The main output of the package is a dataframe containing all the information of these bezier curves.
